thread.title: Corso

author: Corso
title: Corso
text: I really the the quality of the products. The only thing I don't like is the VIP aspect of this to get a better price. I don't need products every month and I am on a budget. Also, There aren't very many great deals for current VIP members. Example the 2 for $24 leggings deal. I wish that would have been for current members as well. This would make me want to cancel my VIP and sign up new to get the deal but I didn't. I would have purchased more.
